in adolescence.

00:13:14.226 --> 00:13:16.996
<i> In the study, published
 in the journal, "Sleep",</i>

00:13:17.096 --> 00:13:18.863 align:start size:81% position:19%
<i> researchers at
 Penn State University</i>

00:13:18.963 --> 00:13:21.800 align:start size:88% position:13%
<i> analyzed data
 for over 2,000 children,</i>

