00:19:57.929 --> 00:20:01.499 align:start size:88% position:13%
<i> A cognitive test designed
 to evaluate attention.</i>

00:20:01.599 --> 00:20:04.069
<i> They also engaged
 in riskier behavior</i>

00:20:04.169 --> 00:20:06.538 align:start size:91% position:9%
<i> using the Balloon Analogue
 Risk Task</i>

00:20:06.638 --> 00:20:10.308 align:start size:88% position:13%
<i> that measures impulsivity
 in decision making.</i>

