00:20:14.078 --> 00:20:15.480 align:start size:66% position:34%
<i> that's a big deal.</i>

00:20:15.580 --> 00:20:17.782 align:start size:63% position:38%
If you're evaluating
treatment options

00:20:17.882 --> 00:20:20.785 align:start size:56% position:44%
for a patient,
that's a big deal.

00:20:20.885 --> 00:20:23.121 align:start size:88% position:13%
<i> (Jaye)
 Kuerston and his
